OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,FThe UK's biggest transport union has
OL,7,Faccused Condor Ferries of exploiting
OL,8,Fforeign sea workers following Jersey's
OL,9,Fdecision to use DFDS Seaways for its
OL,10,Fpassenger and freight services.
OL,12,FThe RMT has described Jersey opting
OL,13,Ffor Danish company DFDS as "an
OL,14,Fimportant step forward in the fight to
OL,15,Fimprove employment standards for
OL,16,Fseafarers".
