OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,FThe union states: "For decades,
OL,7,Fincumbent operator Condor Ferries has
OL,8,Fexploited foreign seafarers on these
OL,9,Fsocially and economically vital routes
OL,10,Fbetween Portsmouth, Poole, and the
OL,11,FChannel Islands."
OL,13,FBrittany Ferries - the main
OL,14,Fshareholder of Condor - has been quick
OL,15,Fto defend its pay standards and
OL,16,F"strong working conditions for
OL,17,Fseafarers".
