OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,FRMT has been vocal about its
OL,7,Fdispleasure with Condor in the past,
OL,8,Fleading strike action against the
OL,9,Fferry service in Portsmouth in 2019.
OL,11,FThe Union states: "Through its
OL,12,Freliance on agency labour, Condor has
OL,13,Fdriven down standards, paying workers
OL,14,Fappallingly low wages. In 2014, the
OL,15,Funion exposed that Ukrainian Ratings
OL,16,Fwere being paid just #2.35 per hour
OL,17,Ffor three-month voyage-only contracts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
