OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,F"Condor's entire fleet is registered
OL,7,Fin the Bahamas under a flag of
OL,8,Fconvenience, a tactic used to avoid
OL,9,Fmeeting UK employment standards and
OL,10,Fone that mirrors the practices of P&O
OL,11,FFerries.
OL,13,F"While Condor, now part-owned by
OL,14,FBrittany Ferries, has been awarded the
OL,15,FGuernsey ferry contract, we will
OL,16,Fcontinue our campaign to ensure
OL,17,Femployment standards improve across
OL,18,Fall Channel Islands routes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
