OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,F"Decent pay, job security, and
OL,7,Fopportunities for apprenticeships must
OL,8,Fbe at the heart of all ferry
OL,9,Foperations."
OL,11,FBrittany Ferries has responded to RMT
OL,12,FUnion's claims, branding them
OL,13,Finaccurate and the timing as "not
OL,14,Fideal".
