OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,FThey state: "Condor was one of the
OL,7,Ffounding signatories to the 2023
OL,8,FVoluntary Seafarers Charter. Signed in
OL,9,Fthe presence of respective transport
OL,10,Fministers from the UK and France, its
OL,11,Fprovisions guarantee minimum pay and
OL,12,Fstrong working conditions for
OL,13,Fseafarers.
OL,15,F"Given this commitment, we don't know
OL,16,Fwhy RMT has chosen today to take a
OL,17,Fswipe at Condor and its crew.
OL,19,F"It's certainly not ideal, coming at a
OL,20,Ftime of understandable concern among
OL,21,Fmany of our loyal seafarer colleagues.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
