OL,3,CUK's biggest union criticise Condor
OL,4,CFerries' working conditions
OL,6,F"Nor is it accurate.
OL,8,F"Perhaps though it is more of a
OL,9,Fmessage for others. Like us, the
OL,10,FUnions will no doubt be closely
OL,11,Fwatching what unfolds elsewhere on the
OL,12,FEnglish Channel in the months and
OL,13,Fyears to come."
